cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

The paper deals with the problem of representing multimodal data for retrieval applications, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.MM are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models, which falls under cs.LG. Additionally, the paper focuses on the task of retrieval, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
